            "content": "<div *ngIf=\"!isLoading && company\">\r\n  <h1>{{ company.name }}</h1>\r\n  <img [src]=\"company.avatar\" alt=\"{{ company.name }}\">\r\n  <p>{{ company.description }}</p>\r\n  <p>Website: <a [href]=\"company.website\" target=\"_blank\">{{ company.website }}</a></p>\r\n\r\n  <h2>Tuyển dụng</h2>\r\n  <div *ngFor=\"let job of jobs | slice:(currentPage*pageSize):(currentPage+1)*pageSize\">\r\n    <h3>{{ job.name || job.title }}</h3>\r\n    <p>Địa điểm: {{ job.province || 'Chưa cập nhật' }}</p>\r\n    <p>Lương: {{ job.salary || 'Thỏa thuận' }}</p>\r\n    <p>Mô tả: {{ job.des || job.description }}</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <div class=\"pagination\">\r\n    <button [disabled]=\"currentPage===0\" (click)=\"onPageChange(currentPage-1)\">‹</button>\r\n    <span>{{currentPage+1}} / {{totalPages}}</span>\r\n    <button [disabled]=\"currentPage>=totalPages-1\" (click)=\"onPageChange(currentPage+1)\">›</button>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div *ngIf=\"isLoading\">\r\n  <p>Đang tải dữ liệu...</p>\r\n</div>\r\n"
